{"tid":2249739,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"2020全球最有價值的100個科技品牌排行榜","createTime":"2020-10-19T14:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T14:00:54.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"072088bc71fad0ef3ce514147d65eb28b9b43be0","tid":2249739,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"英國品牌評估機構Brand Finance發佈了「2020全球最有價值的100大科技品牌」(Tech 100 2020)榜單。其中，$亞馬遜(<a href=\"http://AMZN.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAMZN.US&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZuExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=da24fd34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AMZN.US</a>)$名列榜首，其品牌價值近2208億美元創造歷史記錄。<br />\n<br />\n進入前十名的品牌還有$谷歌(<a href=\"http://GOOG.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGOOG.US&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZuExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=5aab7ecf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">GOOG.US</a>)$、$蘋果(<a href=\"http://AAPL.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAAPL.US&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZuExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=bf90004e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AAPL.US</a>)$、$微軟(<a href=\"http://MSFT.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMSFT.US&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZuExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=6af1136f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">MSFT.US</a>)$、$Facebook(<a href=\"http://FB.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FFB.US&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZuExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=3910a1dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">FB.US</a>)$、三星、華為、微信、Youtube和騰訊QQ。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/20201018000725652677dcc5c4e.png/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F20201018000725652677dcc5c4e.png%2Fbig&h=1a0ea1aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBrand Finace表示，2002年，受COVID-19大流行影響，科技行業喜憂參半。電子商務品牌可能會蓬勃發展。在2020年品牌金融科技100強排名中，電子科技品牌佔品牌總價值的27%。新冠肺炎對媒體和遊戲行業的影響可能有限。<br />\n<br />\n統計結果顯示，100個科技品牌中，最有價值的三大軟件品牌是谷歌、微軟、$甲骨文(<a href=\"http://ORCL.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FORCL.US&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZuExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=a3679882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ORCL.US</a>)$；最有價值的三大電子品牌是蘋果、三星、華為；最有價值的三大電子商務品牌是亞馬遜、淘寶、天貓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/2020101800072561a9054373abf.png/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F2020101800072561a9054373abf.png%2Fbig&h=464295a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，在該榜單的前十大最強品牌中，$騰訊控股(<a href=\"http://00700.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00700.HK&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZuExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=6a934719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00700.HK</a>)$旗下微信以92.9分(滿分100)的品牌實力指數(BSI)居首，對應品牌實力評級為AAA+。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/2020101800072562559aa628c98.png/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F2020101800072562559aa628c98.png%2Fbig&h=8d9a7376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n100個上榜品牌的總價值為18172億美元，其中美國品牌佔總價值64.6%。此外，共有19箇中國科技品牌上榜，排名最高（第七位）的華為品牌價值650.84億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://postimg.futunn.com/20201018000725634ac2eebe980.png/big\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpostimg.futunn.com%2F20201018000725634ac2eebe980.png%2Fbig&h=5547cc6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://brandirectory.com/download-report/brand-finance-tech-100-2020-preview.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbrandirectory.com%2Fdownload-report%2Fbrand-finance-tech-100-2020-preview.pdf&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZuExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=93c0a3e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://brandirectory.com/download-report/brand-finance-tech-100-2020-preview.pdf</a>"}]}